T02TD3663E:267a-1: badzra shr'i kham le s'a dha nam /
T02TD3663E:267a-3: rdo rje lu gu rgyud kyi sgrub thabs /
T02TD3663E:267a-4: bcom ldan 'das ma rdo rje lu gu rgyud la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3663E:267a-5: sngar bstan pa'i cho gas snying gar zla ba'i dkyil 'khor la h'um gi yi ge ljang gu las grub pa'i rdo rje lu gu rgyud zhal gsum phyag drug ma /
T02TD3663E:267a-6: zhal g-yas pa dang cig shos sngo ba dang dkar ba /
T02TD3663E:267b-0: zhal so so la spyan gsum gsum @267b mnga' ba /
T02TD3663E:267b-1: phyag g-yas gsum na rdo rje dang lcags sgrog dang mda'/
T02TD3663E:267b-2: phyag g-yon gsum na sdigs mdzub dang zhags pa dang /
T02TD3663E:267b-4: sku mdog sngo bsangs su ljang ba /
T02TD3663E:267b-6: rgyan thams cad kyis brgyan pa sems can sdang ba rnams 'joms par byed par bdag nyid bsgoms la phyag rgya bcing bar bya'o //
T02TD3663E:267b-7: de la lag pa gnyis khu tshur so sor bcings la mthe'u chung dang mdzub mo lcags sgrog gi rnam par bcing bar bya'o //
T02TD3663E:267b-9: aom badzra shr'i kham le h'um phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD3663E:267b-11: 'di ni rdo rje lu gu rgyud kyi sgrub thabs /
T02TD3663E:267b-12: slob dpon chen po dzee ta ri dgar las rnam par rgyal bas mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02TD3663E:267b-14: // / rgya gar gyi mkhan po pandi ta su ma ti k'irti dang /
T02TD3663E:267b-15: bod kyi lo ts'a ba mkhas pa mar ba chos kyi dbang phyag gis bsgyur cing zhus te gnas la phab pa'o//
